GlusterSP
~~~~~~~~~

Gluster Storage Platform is a software appliance to create commodity
storage clusters out of Dell, HP, Sun, IBM and whitebox servers. It is
an embedded storage operating system with GlusterFS at its core. Users
can access the storage cluster through NFS, CIFS, FTP(S), HTTP(S) and of
course native GlusterFS over Infiniband, 1GigE and 10GigE network
interconnects.
